I"E<p>A command line client written in Go for Nostr created by fiatjaf.</p>

<p>There is an executable under release.</p>

<h2 id="commands-include">Commands Include:</h2>

<blockquote>
  <ul>
    <li>noscl home</li>
    <li>noscl setprivate <key></key></li>
    <li>noscl sign <event-json></event-json></li>
    <li>noscl verify <event-json></event-json></li>
    <li>noscl public</li>
    <li>noscl publish [–reference=<id>...] [--profile=<id>...] <content></content></id></id></li>
    <li>noscl message [–reference=<id>...] <id> <content></content></id></id></li>
    <li>noscl metadata –name=<name> [--about=<about>] [--picture=<picture>]</picture></about></name></li>
    <li>noscl profile <key></key></li>
    <li>noscl follow <key> [--name=<name>]</name></key></li>
    <li>noscl unfollow <key></key></li>
    <li>noscl event <id></id></li>
    <li>noscl share-contacts</li>
    <li>noscl key-gen</li>
    <li>noscl relay</li>
    <li>noscl relay add <url></url></li>
    <li>noscl relay remove <url></url></li>
    <li>noscl relay recommend <url></url></li>
  </ul>
</blockquote>

